M,N,L,K=1,n and n.bxor or function(M,L)local K,N=1,0 while M>0 and L>0 do local O,J=M%2,L%2 if O~=J then N=N+K end M,L,K=(M-O)/2,(L-J)/2,K*2 end if M<L then M=L end while M>0 do local L=M%2 if L>0 K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]][M[3]]=M[4];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]][M[3]]=K[M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]][M[3]]=K[M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]][M[3]]=M[4];else local b;local e;local J;K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=K[M[3]][M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=M[3];L=L+1;M=N[L];J=M[2];e=K[M[3]];K[J+1]=e;K[J]=e[M[4]];L=L+1;M=N[L];K[M[2]]=M[3];L=L+1;M=N[L];J=M[2]K[J]=K[J](O(K,J+1,M[3]))L=L+1;M=N[L];e=M[3];b=K[e]for
